summaries.short: 'Arrivederci.' (Season Two Premiere) Four years after the carnaval that stained their lives, the Gebaras' legend goes on.
summaries.full: 'Arrivederci.' (Season Two Premiere) Rio de Janeiro, 2009. Four years after the carnaval that stained their lives, the Gebaras' legend goes on. These are new times, and within a fake operation, Claudio, the youngest Gebara brother, arranges the slot machine electronic card smuggling business, which soon might end the hegemony of the illegal bets in the streets of Rio.

summaries.short: 'Paternal Heritage.' Claudio resorts to all means to locate the missing Deo, his right-hand man in slot-chip smuggling.
summaries.full: 'Paternal Heritage.' Claudio resorts to all means to find out Deo's whereabouts. The torture applied on Reinaldo, Síio's employee, is effective; Deo is located and Reinaldo's destiny is forged. Claudio decides to ask his brothers for help and fulfills the promise made to his widow.

summaries.short: 'Elephant, the Animal That Never Forgets.' The Gebara family's problems come to a head; as Carnaval commences, destiny calls.
summaries.full: 'Elephant, the Animal That Never Forgets.' The Gebara family's problems come to a head. Claudinho must decide if he will become a typical violent crime boss. Brown realizes his failures, but struggles with a fatal flaw. In a shocking turn, Nilo finds out how his mother died. Carnaval commences with the boys facing, defying and hiding from their destiny.

summaries.short: 'Rios Kings.' Rafael offers some advice to Nilo; Cris invites his friends to the shed where things take an unexpected turn.
summaries.full: 'Rios Kings.' Thinking that the slot business is substituting the illegal bets in the streets of Rio, Rafael tries to convince Nilo to eliminate a large number of bet points. Meanwhile, Claudio's son Cris invites a group of friends to play slots at the shed, but things take an unexpected turn. Brown prepares to launch a new stage in the Samba School.

summaries.short: 'Bear Hug.' Joel murders a man to protect Nilo; Claudinho questions the loyalty of a family member.
summaries.full: 'Bear Hug.' When Anesio runs into the man he had ordered Joel to kill many years before, he commands Nilo to finish the job Joel started. However, to protect Nilo, Joel murders the man instead. Meanwhile, Claudinho starts questioning a family member's loyalty, and Brown further recedes into his drunken haze, shying away from all his responsibilities.

summaries.short: The Gebaras are getting ready to celebrate Christmas. A romance begins between Gloria and Claudio.
summaries.full: The Gebaras are getting ready to celebrate Christmas. A romance begins between Gloria and Claudio. Comodoro, becoming impatient, activates his contacts with the police and sets his revenge on foot. Claudio, Nilo, and Brown are detained and taken to prison for crimes of tax evasion and gearing a criminal gang.

summaries.short: 'Lion, the King of the Animals.' After a sale goes awry, Claudinho is forced to pay the remainder of Anesinho's debt.
summaries.full: 'Lion, the King of the Animals.' The Gebara family struggles to make weekly payments on the late Anesinho's debt, the possible cause of his suicide. After a sale of the rights to a soccer player goes awry, Claudinho must immediately pay the remaining sum. Through it all, he starts becoming the good father that Anesio never was and Brown seems incapable of being.
